title: 111_s2506
content: Section 1 of the Act mandates U.S. Customs and Border Protection to liquidate or reliquidate certain entries of artificial foliage duty-free within 90 days of the Act's enactment. Importers will be refunded any duties paid on these entries, along with interest. The affected entries are specified in subsection (b). The entries listed in the table show import dates and port codes for various items.
